{"tid":1870253,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"滴露開左水可以擺幾耐？","createTime":"2020-02-08T16:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T00:20:20.000Z","uid":94075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"58aa0aa5a2c520286cc1737794c2b650d7880b69","tid":1870253,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"買唔到火酒嘅關係<br />\n開左支滴露開水黎用 <br />\n倒落噴壺度看門口 <br />\n入屋噴下衫褲鞋地氈 <br />\n同埋全屋人都番工 <br />\n有時懶開盤水黎抹 <br />\n直接一野噴落去抹仲快<br />\n但想知咁樣可以擺幾耐 <br />\n因為我都開得幾大支下<br />\n如果只可以放一兩日<br />\n咁就買支細壺用"},{"pid":"680579a51243ac6a9f1bd094712cf4694ed56774","tid":1870253,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"8141b0621d62c3dacc1043bf79bc7d8658723970","tid":1870253,"uid":93277,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:49:38.000Z","msg":"驚到咁其實唔好返工唔好出街啦"},{"pid":"8cd4720c4cb1e43c04ad12985ff99febd3011c59","tid":1870253,"uid":94075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8141b0621d62c3dacc1043bf79bc7d8658723970","tid":1870253,"uid":93277,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:49:38.000Z","msg":"驚到咁其實唔好返工唔好出街啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:52:24.000Z","msg":"啱呀 唔差在行轉武漢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9350fb8a47ed74ef0a8445a779f0d0c1312df3e8","tid":1870253,"uid":157720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:52:55.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"ec5aa5c8060f300288e0a52fe767bdbcb14337dc","tid":1870253,"uid":120627,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"8141b0621d62c3dacc1043bf79bc7d8658723970","tid":1870253,"uid":93277,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:49:38.000Z","msg":"驚到咁其實唔好返工唔好出街啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:52:55.000Z","msg":"你都戇鳩 消毒下有乜問題<br />\n你唔好戴口罩啦 不如"},{"pid":"244e13b1acd83d26598bfe441412344704d8714f","tid":1870253,"uid":157720,"like":0,"dislike":0,